          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>OUR house of hair and lady's hand,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-2" n="2">At first did put me to a stand.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-3" n="3">I have it now,── 'tis plain enough,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-4" n="4">Your hairy business is a <hi rend="italics">Muff</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-5" n="5">Your engine fraught with cooling gales,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-6" n="6">At once so like your mast and sails,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-7" n="7">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-8" n="8">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-9" n="9">And for the rhime to <hi rend="italics">you're the man</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-912-62GI-line-10" n="10">What fits it better than a <hi rend="italics">fan</hi>?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
